Cook pasta according to package directions, adding zucchini during last 5 minutes of cooking; drain. Meanwhile heat oil in large skillet over medium heat. Add chicken. Cook and stir 5 to 6 minutes or until no longer pink and juices run clear. Add tomatoes and pasta sauce. Cook and stir 3 minutes or until mixture is hot. Gently toss chicken mixture into pasta. Season with salt and pepper, if desired.